data.description: Great four bed two bath move in ready home. Attached 1 stall garage. Lots of space and storage in this gem. Large family room. Fourth bedroom has no egress window. Updates include new carpet,fresh paint, luxury vinyl flooring in the kitchen, informal dining and bathroom. As well as new fixtures and granite counter-tops. Roof was done in 2017. Wood burning fireplace in the living room . Slider to the deck. Fenced in yard. Nice hardwood floors in the main 3 bedrooms. Call today for your private showing. All measurements are deemed reliable but are not guaranteed.
